original_text: The men of Naphtali's tribe could not chase out the Canaanites who lived in Beth Shemesh and Beth Anath. They too continued to live among the Canaanites in the land. But the Canaanites who lived in Beth Shemesh and Beth Anath had to do hard work for the Israelites.
korean_text: 납달리는 벧세메스 주민과 벧아낫 주민을 쫓아내지 못하고 그 땅의 주민 가나안 족속 가운데 거주하였으나 벧세메스와 벧아낫 주민들이 그들에게 노역을 하였더라

sentences.original_text: could not chase out the Canaanites
who lived in Beth Shemesh and Beth Anath
They too continued to live among the Canaanites
sentences.korean_translation: 그들도 가나안 사람들 가운데 살아가고 있었습니다
